msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[hint]"
msgid "Select the target of mortar barrage"
msgstr "Selecciona el objetivo del bombardeo de mortero."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_officer]/01"
msgid ""
"We must continue moving, secure that outpost so our advance can continue."
msgstr ""
"Debemos seguir avanzando, asegurar ese puesto avanzado para que podamos "
"continuar nuestro avance."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_officer]/02"
msgid ""
"Take your platoon and advance and clear the enemy positions ahead of us, you "
"have the support of a nearby mortar company. Do not waste any time, we need "
"to keep moving West."
msgstr ""
"Lleva a tu pelotón, avanza y despeja las posiciones enemigas que tenemos "
"delante. Cuentas con el apoyo de una compañía de morteros cercana. No "
"pierdas tiempo, tenemos que seguir avanzando hacia el oeste."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_officer]/03"
msgid "We have a long way to go and we cannot afford any further delays."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos un largo camino por recorrer y no podemos permitirnos más retrasos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_officer]/04"
msgid ""
"Good job men. Hold here in case the English decide they want this back. The "
"column will now continue moving."
msgstr ""
"Buen trabajo, muchachos. Quédate aquí por si los ingleses deciden que "
"quieren recuperar esto. La columna seguirá avanzando."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_officer]/05"
msgid "Oh god! Where did they come from?! We need to stop them!"
msgstr "¡Dios mío! ¿De dónde han salido? ¡Hay que detenerlos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_officer]/06"
msgid ""
"I’ve received word that some heavy guns are being brought forward! We need "
"to hold out as long as we can while they set up the guns!"
msgstr ""
"¡Me han informado de que están trayendo artillería pesada! ¡Tenemos que "
"aguantar todo lo que podamos mientras la instalan!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_officer]/07"
msgid ""
"A screen of 88s and howitzers have been set up just behind us. You can now "
"fallback and regroup at Mercatel to reinforce them!"
msgstr ""
"Se ha instalado una pantalla de 88 y obuses justo detrás de nosotros. ¡Ahora "
"pueden retroceder y reagruparse en Mercatel para reforzarlos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_officer]/08"
msgid ""
"Take command of the 88s set up just outside Mercatel. We need to stop the "
"enemy armored assault before they reach the town and cut deeper into our "
"lines!"
msgstr ""
"Toma el mando de los 88 situados a las afueras de Mercatel. ¡Tenemos que "
"detener el ataque blindado enemigo antes de que alcancen la ciudad y se "
"adentren más en nuestras líneas!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_officer]/09"
msgid ""
"Gute arbeit, männer. The Tommies are running away! They won't come back "
"anytime soon while the Luftwaffe is in the sky!"
msgstr ""
"Buen trabajo, muchachos. ¡Los Tommies están huyendo! ¡No volverán pronto "
"mientras la Luftwaffe siga en el cielo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_soldier]/01"
msgid ""
"Herr leutnant! Our forward Aufklärer spotted some Tommies dug in around the "
"town ahead of us. What are your orders?"
msgstr ""
"¡Herr Leutnant! Nuestros Aufklärer avanzados han avistado a algunos Tommies "
"atrincherados en la ciudad que tenemos delante. ¿Cuáles son tus órdenes?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_soldier]/02"
msgid "Panzer Alarm! Tanks coming from the North-West!"
msgstr "¡Achtung Panzer! ¡Tanques procedentes del noroeste!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_soldier]/03"
msgid ""
"Their armor is too thick! We're doing nothing to them! Aim at the tracks and "
"immobilise them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Su blindaje es demasiado grueso! ¡No les estamos haciendo nada! ¡Apuntad a "
"las orugas y inmovilizadlos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_soldier]/04"
msgid ""
"The British artillery is trying to hit one of our Acht-Acht's! Move it to a "
"new position before they zero in on it!"
msgstr ""
"¡La artillería británica está intentando alcanzar uno de nuestros Acht-Acht! "
"¡Muévelo a una nueva posición antes de que lo localicen!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_soldier]/05"
msgid ""
"Take grenades and explosives from this crate!  Use anything you can find! We "
"must stop them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Coged granadas y explosivos de esta caja! ¡Utilizad todo lo que encontréis! "
"¡Debemos detenerlos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[narrators]/"
"[narrator_soldier]/06"
msgid "Planes incoming!... Wait, it's our boys! They will show them now!"
msgstr ""
"¡Aviones acercándose!... ¡Esperen, son nuestros muchachos! ¡Ahora les van a "
"dar una lección!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[reinforcements]/mortars"
msgid "Mortar barrage"
msgstr "Bombardeo de mortero"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[scenario]/phase2"
msgid "2 hours later..."
msgstr "Dos horas más tarde..."

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[tasks]/task01"
msgid "Eliminate British forward positions"
msgstr "Eliminar las posiciones avanzadas británicas."

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[tasks]/task02"
msgid "Stop enemy tanks before they reach our temporary HQ!"
msgstr ""
"¡Detén los tanques enemigos antes de que lleguen a nuestro cuartel general "
"temporal!"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[tasks]/task03"
msgid "Repulse the enemy counter-attack!"
msgstr "¡Repele el contraataque enemigo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[tasks]/task_secret01"
msgid "Secret objective #1"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[tasks]/"
"task_secret01_completed"
msgid "Secret objective #1: Shoot a turret off a Matilda I tank"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto n.º 1: Derribar una torreta de un tanque Matilda I."

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/[timer]/timer_phase2"
msgid "Do not let the enemy tanks reach the field HQ:"
msgstr ""
"No dejes que los tanques enemigos lleguen al cuartel general del campo:"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/name"
msgid "Fall Gelb"
msgstr "Operación Amarillo"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/name_big"
msgid "Fall Gelb"
msgstr "Operación Amarillo"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Wunderbar! Your improvisation skills have stopped the British counterattack, "
"which means the ghost division can continue racing to the Channel coast. "
"Well done, and keep going!"
msgstr ""
"¡Genial! Tus habilidades de improvisación han detenido el contraataque "
"británico, lo que significa que la división fantasma puede seguir avanzando "
"hacia la costa del Canal de la Mancha. ¡Bien hecho, sigue así!"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"This is serious; our advance has come to a halt because the British tanks "
"have broken the encirclement we almost established. We cannot afford to push "
"forward anymore. This is a serious setback!"
msgstr ""
"Esto es grave; nuestro avance se ha detenido porque los tanques británicos "
"han roto el cerco que casi habíamos establecido. No podemos permitirnos "
"seguir avanzando. ¡Es un grave revés!"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/date"
msgid "May 21st, 1940 · Arras, Hauts-de-France, France"
msgstr "21 de mayo de 1940 · Arras, Altos de Francia, Francia"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/place"
msgid "7th Panzer Division"
msgstr "7.ª División Panzer"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1940_05_arras/story"
msgid ""
"Just 11 days ago, Europe went from ‘Sitzkrieg’ to ‘Blitzkrieg’ with the "
"rapid advance of German troops into the Netherlands, Belgium, and "
"Luxembourg.\n"
"\n"
" Taking everyone by surprise, the Germans quickly cross the Meuse River at "
"Sedan just days later and push West. \n"
"\n"
"Exploiting the element of surprise, the 7th Panzer Division has been on the "
"move for 8 days straight. Right now, you are approaching Agny, south of "
"Arras. \n"
"\n"
" We have just found a British strongpoint that is blocking our way. \n"
"\n"
" Take the lead and clear that up quickly, so we can maintain momentum and "
"drive forward to the Channel Coast."
msgstr ""
"Hace solo 11 días, Europa pasó de la «guerra de posiciones» a la «guerra "
"relámpago» con el rápido avance de las tropas alemanas hacia los Países "
"Bajos, Bélgica y Luxemburgo. Sorprendiendo a todos, los alemanes cruzaron "
"rápidamente el río Mosa en Sedán pocos días después y avanzaron hacia el "
"oeste. \n"
"\n"
"Aprovechando el factor sorpresa, la 7.ª División Panzer lleva 8 días "
"consecutivos en movimiento. En este momento, te estás acercando a Agny, al "
"sur de Arras. Acabamos de encontrar un bastión británico que nos bloquea el "
"paso. Toma la iniciativa y despeja rápidamente el camino para que podamos "
"mantener el impulso y avanzar hacia la costa del Canal de la Mancha."
